▪️Tattoo removal pt I. 
More than 10 years later, getting my first tattoo removed. I was thinking about it for a while and finally decided to do it. First impressions, it is more painful and takes much more time to get the tattoo removed than get it done, but even after the first (painful😬) session I can see it disappearing. I was lucky to find @skincitylabnyc who made me feel very comfortable and were patient with me whenever I needed small breaks during the process.☺️🫶🏻 More sessions to come.✔️
